    "content": "<p>For the block diagram shown in the figure, the transfer function $${{Y(s)} \\over {R(s)}}$$ is</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lyy5oqdg/cdc3826e-bb07-41a8-9d2b-bb1318217dbc/dc5be440-48cd-11ef-9c03-5b7518daaafa/file-jaoe38c1lyy5oqdh.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lyy5oqdg/cdc3826e-bb07-41a8-9d2b-bb1318217dbc/dc5be440-48cd-11ef-9c03-5b7518daaafa/file-jaoe38c1lyy5oqdh.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE EE 2023 Control Systems - Block Diagram and Signal Flow Graph Question 3 English\"></p>",
