    "content": "<p>$$ \\text { For the closed-loop system shown, the transfer function } \\frac{E(s)}{R(s)} \\text { is } $$</p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mh5z27ac/498330a1-80e3-4f59-be2e-31d9685761c4/1d0e0240-b176-11f0-a8fc-1beb57a635e8/file-jaoe38c1mh5z27ad.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mh5z27ac/498330a1-80e3-4f59-be2e-31d9685761c4/1d0e0240-b176-11f0-a8fc-1beb57a635e8/file-jaoe38c1mh5z27ad.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE EE 2021 Control Systems - Block Diagram and Signal Flow Graph Question 1 English\">",
